  "response": "Kit Kat bars do not typically contain peanuts as part of their standard ingredients. However, they are produced in facilities that also process peanuts and other allergens, which means there is a risk of cross-contamination. If you have a peanut allergy or are concerned about allergens, it\u2019s always best to check the packaging for the most current ingredient information and allergen warnings or consult the manufacturer's website for the latest details.",
